* Ebisu Shrine – Enshrined deity: {{ill|lt=Ebisu|Q1129330|WD=Q1129330|lt=Ebisu-no-Kami}}
* Tenmangū Shrine – Enshrined deity: {{ill|lt=Sugawara no Michizane|Q382005|WD=Q382005}}
* Hachiman Shrine – Enshrined deity: {{ill|lt=Emperor Ōjin|Q317997|WD=Q317997}}
* Amaterasu Ōmikami Shrine – Enshrined deity: {{ill|lt=Amaterasu|Q455602|WD=Q455602}}
* Susanoo Shrine – Enshrined deity: {{ill|lt=Susanoo|Q272993|WD=Q272993|lt=Susanoo-no-Mikoto}}
* Mizuhanome Shrine (みずはのめじんじゃ) – Enshrined deity: {{ill|lt=Mizuhanome||WD=|lt=Mizuhanome-no-Kami}}
* Takafusa Shrine – Enshrined deities: {{ill|lt=Futsunushi-no-Kami|Q1107286|WD=Q1107286}} and {{ill|lt=Takemikazuchi|Q1502690|WD=Q1502690|lt=Takemikazuchi-no-Kami}}
* Imamiya Shrine – Enshrined deity: {{ill|lt=Susanoo|Q272993|WD=Q272993|lt=Susanoo-no-Mikoto}}
* Inari Shrine – Enshrined deity: {{ill|lt=Ukanomitama|Q3080728|WD=Q3080728|lt=Ukanomitama-no-Kami}}

'''Shrines outside the grounds'''
