* Amaterasu Ōmikami Shrine – Enshrined deity: {{ill|lt=Amaterasu|Q455602|WD=Q455602|1=Amaterasu}}
* Susanoo Shrine – Enshrined deity: {{ill|lt=Susanoo|Q272993|WD=Q272993|lt=Susanoo-no-Mikoto|1=Susanoo-no-Mikoto}}
